{"tid":852514,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"偉華逆市錄破頂 呎價2萬","createTime":"2018-10-08T02:03:24.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-08T02:28:24.000Z","uid":130169,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"ff9d330d7ccffa5840ef65993806329320e5179f","tid":852514,"uid":130169,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-08T02:03:24.000Z","msg":"【明報專訊】雖然近日二手物業市場錄得不少減價成交，惟部分物業減價後，呎價仍然破頂，其中沙田偉華中心一個細單位，最新以599萬元售出，實呎破2萬元創屋苑新高；市場消息指，上述偉華中心2座高層G室，實用297方呎，原業主最初叫價650萬元，最終減價至599萬元售出，即累減51萬元或約8%，但實呎仍高見20,168元，創屋苑呎價新高紀錄。據悉，原業主早於2007年以142萬元購入單位，持貨11年帳面獲利457萬元，賺幅高達3.2倍。"},{"pid":"ead40e75ba9e15396c52006c84a361179515c425","tid":852514,"uid":174420,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-08T02:04:08.000Z","msg":"租租又贏<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b2a3e808a0019ce6533f71d30d6e26163ee1dbaf","tid":852514,"uid":38461,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-08T02:04:30.000Z","msg":"偉華都20000萬一呎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ea1fe86aae063e0c7e275e092f7c39dd0446023a","tid":852514,"uid":156652,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-08T02:04:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Oq86spu.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FOq86spu.jpg&h=fe66f1c1&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"78f2e8b0c5c3f3a7e510626c6bf5a472f317353d","tid":852514,"uid":130169,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-08T02:13:27.000Z","msg":"沙田唔計"},{"pid":"0f7fc1160f117a7cdaa5125eba17e68d5de06361","tid":852514,"uid":147367,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-08T02:16:58.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">樓市大劈價</span></span><br />\n<br />\n近日二手物業市場錄得不少減價成交，其中沙田偉華中心一個細單位，最新以599萬元售出；市場消息指，上述偉華中心2座高層G室，實用297方呎，原業主最初叫價650萬元，最終減價至599萬元售出，即累減51萬元或約8%。"},{"pid":"